  <brief_title>Early Changes in Positron Emissions Tomography (PET/CT) Scan as Predictors of Clinical Outcome in NSCLC Treated With EGFR Tyrosin Kinase Inhibitors (TKI)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Early Changes in 18F-fluorodeoxyglucose Positron Emissions Tomography (18F-FDG-PET/CT) Scan as Predictors of Clinical Outcome in NSCLC Treated With EGFR Tyrosin Kinase Inhibitors (TKI)</official_title>
